    <ImplicitInverseRef name="keySeries" id="800729df-74ba-4ab3-a64f-43b433caaa22">
        <embedded/>
        <type name="CM_KeySeriesByCodeDict"/>
        <text>


CM_Bank is used for 3 different entities - Business Units, Companies and the Root Company.

This attribute is used by Business Unit



In invoicing the audit sequence number is controlled by the ROOT CM_Bank using the KeySeries key SN_AUDIT

In invoicing the charge sequence number is controlled by the ROOT CM_Bank using the KeySeries key SN_CHARGE

In invoicing the invoice line sequence number is controlled by the ROOT CM_Bank using the KeySeries key SN_INVOICELINE

In invoicing the invoice sequence number is controlled by the Business Unit CM_Bank using the KeySeries key SN_INVOICE
</text>
    </ImplicitInverseRef>
